org.hibernate.query.sqm.consume.multitable.spi.idtable.IdTable

  • Packages that use IdTable 
    Package Description
    org.hibernate.dialect
    This package abstracts the SQL dialect of the underlying database.
    org.hibernate.query.sqm.consume.multitable.spi.idtable
    Support for IdTableStrategy implementations which are backed by an "id table" which is used to temporarily store the ids of entities matching the update/delete restrictions.
